  "title": "End-to-End Release, Incident Recovery, and Engineering Defense",
  "description": "A candidate passes unit tests but lacks clean-build, race, accessibility, fair-use, failure, migration, rollback, restore, and stakeholder evidence, while residual risks have no owners. Learners cumulatively produce defensible recoverable Go Pokedex release dossier through theory, guided work, debugging, transfer, retrieval, and assessment.",
